in-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/3493/', '', 'Clemastine, Mepyramine, Diphenhydramine, Tripelennamine, Doxepin, Pheniramine, Promethazine, Bacitracin, Flurbiprofen, Ibuprofen, Chlorhexidine, More', 'Lidocaine, Zinc sulfate, Tetracaine, Zinc acetate, Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluocinonide, Zinc chloride, Procaine, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, Zinc gluconate, More', 1767369485);
